  "prompt": "Will the celebrities who promised to move if Trump won, really leave the US?",
  "response": "There have been various celebrities who have joked or expressed the sentiment of leaving the U.S. if Donald Trump won the presidency. However, it's common for such statements to be more about expressing frustration or political dissent rather than actual intent to move. \n\nIn past elections, some celebrities who made similar promises either did not follow through or were later seen continuing to live and work in the U.S. Ultimately, whether they choose to leave or stay can depend on many factors, including personal circumstances, career opportunities, and political climate changes. Each individual's decision would be their own, and it's often difficult to predict such outcomes based on prior statements.",
